history.content:
Key Date:

The deadline for Spring 2019 DeCal course proposals to be turned in to the appropriate Department Chair's Assistant is Wednesday, October 24th.

** Electronic, late, or incomplete submissions will not be considered. **

  • EE DeCal proposals should be submitted to 225 Cory Hall.
  • CS DeCal proposals should be submitted to 389 Soda Hall.

To learn more about the process for proposing and setting up an EECS DeCal, please see:

https://eecs.berkeley.edu/resources/undergrads/decal
